thread.title_full: BRIEF-GM says Sept China vehicle sales -3.9 percent y/y | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-GM says Sept China vehicle sales -3.9 percent y/y
text:
Oct 12 General Motors Co says:
* Sept China vehicle sales total 295,236, -3.9 percent y/y, versus -4.8 percent in August
* Jan-Sept China vehicle sales total 2.5 million, +1.6 percent y/y Source text: [ bit.ly/1MmC1jF ] Further company coverage: (Reporting By Jake Spring)
